We are still sending them out but we are very busy with a lot of stuff.Unfortunatly there are always people who aren't fair and subscribed to our airdrop multiple times. Like the person selling 25k DGX on Forkdelta. The person received 5x the airdrop of 5k and sent them to 1 address. We will put a red flag on these addresses for the next drop. We will do our best to filter these people out in the following airdrop, and to be fair to the honest people we decided to drop extra coins, and instead of 600 people the next drop will be 750 participants. We reserved 2x 3 million tokens but we will add the needed tokens from our own reserves. We will do our best to make DigiDex fair and square to all. Always FOR and BY our community!
